section
  h3(id='res.status') res.status(code)
  
  p.
    Chainable alias of node's <code>res.statusCode</code>. Use this method to set the HTTP status for the response.

  +js.
    res.status(403).end();
    res.status(400).send('Bad Request');
    res.status(404).sendFile('/absolute/path/to/404.png');
